  "privacyIntro": "At Ines Shop, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our mobile application.",
  "privacySection1Title": "1. Information We Collect",
  "privacySection1Body": "We collect information you provide directly, such as your name, email address, phone number, profile picture, and shipping addresses. We also collect order history and payment-related information necessary to process your purchases.",
  "privacySection2Title": "2. How We Use Your Information",
  "privacySection2Body": "Your information is used to process orders, manage your account, provide customer support, send order updates, and improve our services. We do not sell your personal data to third parties.",
  "privacySection3Title": "3. Data Storage and Security",
  "privacySection3Body": "Your data is stored securely using industry-standard encryption and security practices. Profile images and product images are hosted via Cloudinary, and authentication is managed through Clerk's secure infrastructure.",
  "privacySection4Title": "4. Your Rights",
  "privacySection4Body": "You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time through the Edit Profile section of the app. You may also request complete account deletion by contacting our support team.",
  "privacySection5Title": "5. Contact Us",
  "privacySection5Body": "If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, please contact us through the Help Center or Contact Us section of the app.",

  "termsIntro": "Welcome to Ines Shop. By accessing or using our mobile application, you agree to be bound by the following Terms of Service. Please read them carefully.",
